745
00:57:53,980 --> 00:57:55,210
Vieš...

746
00:57:56,040 --> 00:57:58,310
Aký je rozdiel medzi Min Joon Gookom
a Park Soo Haom?

747
00:57:58,310 --> 00:58:00,520
Nie, neviem.

748
00:58:00,800 --> 00:58:02,670
A ani to nechcem vedieť.

749
00:58:08,780 --> 00:58:10,000
Pane!

750
00:58:10,490 --> 00:58:12,020
<i>Min Joon Gook...</i>

751
00:58:12,020 --> 00:58:13,330
<i>Nemal nikoho.</i>

752
00:58:14,220 --> 00:58:16,310
<i>Nikoho, kto by mu veril...</i>

753
00:58:16,640 --> 00:58:18,400
<i>Nikoho, kto by si ho vypočul...</i>

754
00:58:19,100 --> 00:58:21,180
<i>A nikoho, kto by ho miloval.</i>

755
00:58:22,370 --> 00:58:24,430
Jang Hye Sung! Jang Hye Sung!

756
00:58:25,520 --> 00:58:26,610
<i>A tiež...</i>

757
00:58:26,810 --> 00:58:28,830
<i>Nemal nikoho, koho by chcel ochrániť.</i>

758
00:58:31,900 --> 00:58:33,670
<i>Ak by mal vo svojom život aspoň jednu osobu...</i>

759
00:58:34,480 --> 00:58:36,800
<i>Min Joon Gook mohol žiť úplne inak.</i>

760
00:58:37,970 --> 00:58:39,480
<i>Tak ako Park Soo Ha.</i>

761
00:58:40,700 --> 00:58:42,160
<i>Preto Min Joon Gooka...</i>

762
00:58:42,710 --> 00:58:44,070
<i>Tak trochu...</i>

763
00:58:44,790 --> 00:58:45,930
<i>Ľutujem.</i>

764
00:58:56,910 --> 00:58:58,450
Ty hlupák.

